Log:Selective is a Perl module for selective logging to the console.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

DEPENDENCIES

	Exporter, constant

This module should also work under Windows if Win32::Console::ANSI is installed.

DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Log::Selective

